data-triple-N3.o: "A kindergarten is a preschool educational institution for children. The term was created by Friedrich Frobel for the play and activity institute that he created in 1837 in Bad Blankenburg as a social experience for children for their transition from home to school. His goal was that children should be taken care of and nourished in "children's gardens" like plants in a garden."@en
